00:04:33.833 --> 00:04:35.750
Not everybody has a car
to keep everything in.

00:04:35.750 --> 00:04:37.317
So it's nice to
have fewer products.

00:04:37.317 --> 00:04:38.650
You don't have touch up as much.

00:04:38.650 --> 00:04:41.150
For a girl on the go,
it's the perfect solution.

00:04:41.150 --> 00:04:45.410
So we finally came out with
these great Pro Longwear

00:04:45.410 --> 00:04:48.660
Lipglasses that are
saturated with color,

00:04:48.660 --> 00:04:53.620
